snippet.textDisplay: Maithili Thakur and Ravi Kishen added the true colors of Holi into this song. Sitar by Ayaan & Aman Bangaash brothers - reminds us of their father Amjad Ali Khan’s renditions. Percussion with harmonium sound captures the vibe and essence of Avadh ki Holi , just the right bass and alaap.
